omponents such as outcome-based education, a Choice Credit System (CBCS). Across its seven schools, the university offers a robust array of undergraduate and postgraduate programs to cultivate academic excellence and practical proficiency.\nSandip University's educational philosophy emphasizes mandatory internship courses, providing hands-on experience in real-world settings relevant to students' fields of study. The internships enhance understanding of industry practices and foster crucial skills. The university also emphasizes foreign language education to broaden students' perspectives and enhance cross-cultural communication skills, recognizing the global nature of modern workplaces.\nFurthermore, Sandip University's commitment to holistic education extends to integrating interdisciplinary learning pathways, open electives, and skill enhancement courses within the CBCS framework. These initiatives empower students to tailor their educational journeys according to their interests and career goals, ensuring they graduate with academic credentials and the practical skills and cultural competencies necessary for success in today's diverse and dynamic world.\nAligned with the National Education Policy (NEP) 2020, the university has recently revamped its academic structure to include interdisciplinary learning pathways and multiple entry and exit points within the CBCS framework. This initiative empowers students to tailor their educational journeys, opt for honors or research-focused programs, and explore diverse subjects beyond their core disciplines. Moreover, Sandip University integrates open electives and skill enhancement courses into its curriculum, enabling students to pursue additional interests and acquire supplementary skills that complement their career aspirations.\nIn addition to academic rigor, the university emphasizes holistic development through Ability Enhancement Courses (AEC), Value Education Courses (VEC), and Indian Knowledge System (IKS) courses. These components enrich students' learning experiences by promoting ethical values, cultural awareness, and a deep understanding of societal responsibilities. By embracing these innovative educational strategies, Sandip University continues to uphold its commitment to nurturing well-rounded individuals who are prepared to excel in a rapidly evolving global landscape.\nOur faculty members are selected from esteemed institutions across India and worldwide. They bring knowledge and intellectual rigor to the classroom, with backgrounds from renowned institutions such as IITs and NITs. Our faculty are passionate educators and active researchers engaged in cutting-edge projects. They inspire and empower students to achieve their full potential in a vibrant, supportive learning environment.\n[ Enquire Now ](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/admission.php>)\n| [Call Now](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<tel:1800-212-2714>)\n#### Quick Info\n  * [UGC Notices](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/ugc-notices.php>)\n  * [Events](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/blog/events/>)\n  * [Approvals](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/approvals.php>)\n  * [Institutional Membership](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/membership.php>)\n  * [Media Coverage](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/media-coverage.php>)\n  * [UGC Gallery](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/ugc-gallery.php>)\n  * [Testimonials](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/placements/testimonials-stud.php>)\n\n\n#### Useful Links\n  * [National Fee Structure](https://www.sandipuniversity.edu.in/academics/<https:/www.sandipuniversity.edu.